">5.28am <span class=\"timezone\">ET</span></time> </p>    <div class=\"block-elements\">  <p>• This article was amended on 1 October 2013 to correct a reference to Iraq&apos;s &quot;nuclear stockpile&quot; to &quot;chemical stockpile&quot; and to clarify a summary of remarks that Rouhani made about the use of chemical weapons in Syria</p> </div>   </div> <div id=\"block-52420b71e4b082870c28e0a8\" class=\"block is-summary\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2013-09-24T23:19:28.230+01:00\">6.19pm <span class=\"timezone\">ET</span></time> </p>   <h2 class=\"block-title\">Summary</h2>  <div class=\"block-elements\">  <p>We&apos;re going to wrap up our live blog coverage for the day. </p> <p>• A summary of Iranian president Hassan Rouhani&apos;s speech before the general assembly <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/sep/24/un-general-assembly-obama-rouhani-rousseff-live#block-5242043ce4b092830eda27ce\">is here</a>.</p> <p>• A summary of US president Barack Obama&apos;s speech <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/sep/24/un-general-assembly-obama-rouhani-rousseff-live#block-5241a95de4b073439ec092fa\">is here</a>.</p> <p>• A general summary of today&apos;s proceedings at the United Nations <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/world/2013/sep/24/un-general-assembly-obama-rouhani-rousseff-live#block-5241ecd4e4b025976cb65bc4\">is here</a>. </p> <p>UPDATE:</p>  <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/margbrennan/statuses/382622128886923264\">  <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>English text of the Rouhani speech: <a href=\"http://t.co/n20g7mOyM7\">http://t.co/n20g7mOyM7</a></p>&mdash; margaret brennan (@margbrennan) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/margbrennan/statuses/382622128886923264\">September 24, 2013</a></blockquote>  </figure> </div>   <p class=\"block-time updated-time\">Updated <time datetime=\"2013-09-24T23:27:32.596+01:00\">at 6.27pm ET</time></p>  </div> <div id=\"block-52420a83e4b092830eda27d0\" class=\"block is-key-event\"> <p class=\"block-time published-time\"> <time datetime=\"2013-09-24T23:00:16.052+01:00\">6.00pm <span class=\"timezone\">ET</span></time> </p>   <h2 class=\"block-title\">Reactions</h2>  <div class=\"block-elements\">  <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/ThomasErdbrink/statuses/382625909020172288\">  <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>With all eyes on Rouhani and so many people not understanding his key speech, his team has missed an opportunity - analyst tells me.</p>&mdash; Thomas Erdbrink (@ThomasErdbrink) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ThomasErdbrink/statuses/382625909020172288\">September 24, 2013</a></blockquote>  </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/Ali_Gharib/statuses/382619500094296064\">  <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Rouhani&#39;s speech was anti-climactic. Not much there there: no specifics, no confrontation... <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Iran&amp;src=hash\">#Iran</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23UNGA&amp;src=hash\">#UNGA</a></p>&mdash; Ali Gharib (@Ali_Gharib) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ali_Gharib/statuses/382619500094296064\">September 24, 2013</a></blockquote>  </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/SaeedKD/statuses/382615967945072640\">  <blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p>Me neither: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/NegarMortazavi\">@NegarMortazavi</a>: I&#39;m not too impressed yet. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23Rouhani&amp;src=hash\">#Rouhani</a> at the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23UNGA&amp;src=hash\">#UNGA</a>.</p>&mdash; Saeed Kamali Dehghan (@SaeedKD) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SaeedKD/statuses/382615967945072640\">September 24, 2013</a></blockquote>  </figure>  <figure class=\"element element-tweet\" data-canonical-url=\"https://twitter.com/ThomasErdbrink/statuses/38261821543